   254                              <1> getSFTShareInfo:
   255                              <1> ;Get SFT sharing information about file.
   256                              <1> ;Input: rdx -> DPL (use ebx and ecx)
   257                              <1> ;       DPL.ebx = MFT Index (1 based)
   258                              <1> ;       DPL.ecx = SFT Index (1 based)
   259                              <1> ;Output:
   260                              <1> ;   CF=NC: File found 
   261                              <1> ;       rdi -> ASCIIZ filename
   262                              <1> ;       ebx = dMID for the SFT
   263                              <1> ;       ecx = Number of locks held by SFT
   264                              <1> ;   CF=CY: Either index is out of range.
   265                              <1> ;       eax = No more files
